Bomber- (5)
- The bomber, when ever killed by a member of another faction, attacks a certain number of people before dying.
- The bomber can pick a total of 3 people to kill. They can pick a person every night and once picked, the targets cannot be changed.
- If the Bomber is ever killed by a member of another faction, all the other people they have chosen will be weak attacked. These attacks are counted as visits.
- The bomber can pick new targets once they have died and respawned. The bomber dying because of tribute will not trigger their ability.
- Picking a target is immediate, and the targets are killed at the same time as when the bomber is killed.
- Respawns in 6 phases.
